WEBVTT

00:00.023 --> 00:01.959
Previously on "Once Upon a Time"...

00:01.984 --> 00:05.068
The Evil Queen sent everyone
from the Enchanted Forest here.

00:05.093 --> 00:06.058
That's what you're going with?

00:06.093 --> 00:07.359
It's true.

00:07.394 --> 00:08.994
- How long will you be with us?
- A week.

00:09.030 --> 00:09.928
It's your destiny.

00:09.964 --> 00:12.397
You're gonna bring
back the happy endings.

00:12.432 --> 00:13.965
I do hope you like apples.

00:14.000 --> 00:14.766
It's poison.

00:14.801 --> 00:15.928
You may not believe in the curse,

00:15.953 --> 00:17.334
but I believe in you.

00:18.499 --> 00:19.498
Henry!

00:19.523 --> 00:21.806
Every story in this
book actually happened.

00:21.831 --> 00:23.330
Goodbye, Emma.

00:24.666 --> 00:26.733
Henry, you were right about the curse.

00:26.768 --> 00:28.000
I should've believed you.

00:33.206 --> 00:35.840
I love you, Henry.

00:41.304 --> 00:43.548
This might be the most
important mission yet...

00:43.584 --> 00:45.016
Operation Best Man.

00:49.722 --> 00:53.991
_

